OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and warm with lengthy sunny
OL,6,Fspells for much of the day, but
OL,7,Fsunshine turning somewhat hazier as
OL,8,Fcloud spreads south in the afternoon.
OL,9,FWarmer in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening with some evening sunshine.
OL,13,FStaying dry overnight with clear
OL,14,Fspells perhaps allowing the odd fog
OL,15,Fpatch, somewhat cloudier in the
OL,16,Fsouthwest.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FIt will be dry throughout the
OL,19,Fday with variable cloud and some warm
OL,20,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
