OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fagain on Tuesday with variable cloud
OL,7,Fand some warm sunny spells. Variable
OL,8,Fcloud and sunny spells on Wednesday
OL,9,Fand Thursday with the odd light shower
OL,10,Fat times. Breezy Thursday.
